<L>__{interior village school. the past . day.}
<A>__{annie reaches for her pen. reverend innes is giving the children their writing lessons, according to "mulhauser's technique"}
<C>__{innes}
<D>__{first positions.}
<A>__{the children assume the position as if in some militaristic drill.}
<C>__{innes}
<D>__{second positions.}
<A>__{grips are adjusted, pens are dipped.}
<C>__{innes}
<D>__{assume the distance.}
<A>__{the children lean back fractionally, so their elbows are just back from the edge of the desk.}
<C>__{innes}
<D>__{.....and begin.}
<A>__{the children start to copy the sentence which innes has written on the blackboard. annie reads the sentence and hesitates: "and on the seventh day god ended his work which he had made; and he rested"}
